That's a whole different issue than it was a temporary timing thing. I would tell you, we would expect rates to be moving up over time, and we expect a rather healthy, very strong economy.

Jennifer Piepszak -- Chief Financial Officer

Yes. Yes. And what we've seen so far on the short end is not unhealthy or something we're worried about. It's a dynamic of so much cash chasing the supply.

